{"tid":778710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太平門當𨋢！拖篋大媽狂按警鐘　嚇窒快餐店食客","createTime":"2018-08-14T01:50:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T15:47:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":485,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"7bcd40a4d3c076195a9e02008f44552ce68618f5","tid":778710,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180814/photo/bkn-20180814073030468-0814_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180814092039\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180814%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180814073030468-0814_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180814092039&h=00208826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太平門被當𨋢門？近日在網上流傳照片，指在一間快餐店內，有內地旅客誤以為太平門是升降機，並按下火警鐘「等候」，場面惹笑。 <br />\n<br />\n網民於星期一（六日）在社交群組「Tai Po 大埔」發貼，指他當日在一間連鎖快餐店的太平門旁等候餐點，未料幾名打算前往二樓的拖篋大媽，突然上前問他：「你按了電梯沒有？」並按了數下門旁的火警鐘。 <br />\n<br />\n發貼者笑言被嚇壞，又慶幸火警鐘沒有反應。貼文引來網民熱烈討論，形容事件「千奇百趣」，又戲言發貼者應「對住佢唱，強人是你」，並笑稱快餐店應張貼告示。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180814/photo/bkn-20180814073030468-0814_00822_001_02p.jpg?20180814092039\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180814%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180814073030468-0814_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20180814092039&h=583e210e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過往曾有內地遊客誤以為地鐵站內的機房鐵門是升降機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180814/bkn-20180814073030468-0814_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180814%2Fbkn-20180814073030468-0814_00822_001.html&d=wTynxmgJSEY%2FRTvDg%2Fr0txv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=b1bdeecd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180814/bkn-20180814073030468-0814_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"60c439605df483e4e5cc501a945c793e5bb69551","tid":778710,"uid":126305,"like":129,"dislike":2,"score":127,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\